ITEM 5.02 DEPARTURE OF DIRECTORS OR PRINCIPAL OFFICERS; ELECTION OF DIRECTORS; APPOINTMENT OF PRINCIPAL OFFICERS.
 
AnnTaylor Stores Corporation issued a press release announcing the election of Barbara Turf to the company's Board of Directors on September 17, 2004 and Ms. Turf's appointment to its Compensation Committee. A copy of the press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and is incorporated herein by reference.
 
ITEM 9.01 FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND EXHIBITS.
 
 
 
 
Pursuant to the requirements of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, the registrant has duly caused this report to be signed on its behalf by the undersigned hereunto duly authorized.
 
 
 
 

Exhibit 99.1
 
 
 
 AnnTaylor Stores Corporation (NYSE: ANN) today announced that Barbara Turf has joined its Board of Directors.
New York, New York, September 17, 2004
 
Ms. Turf is President of Crate & Barrel (Euromarket Designs, Inc.). After taking a summer job at the retailer's first store in Chicago in 1967, she became the manager of the company's second store in Wilmette, Illinois. In 1973, she joined the company's merchandising staff, and since 1978 has held responsibility for overseeing all merchandise buying. Prior to her current appointment in 1996, she was Executive Vice President, Merchandising and Marketing.
 
"We are delighted to welcome Ms. Turf to our Board of Directors," commented J. Patrick Spainhour, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer. "Her 30 years of retail experience along with her deep understanding of the relationship between the client and the brand make her a valuable addition to our Board," he added.
 
Ms. Turf will bring the number of independent directors on Ann Taylor's 8-person Board of Directors to 7. Ms. Turf will also serve as a member of the fully independent Compensation Committee.
 
Ann Taylor is one of the country's leading women's specialty retailers, operating 699 stores in 45 states, the District of Columbia and Puerto Rico, and also Online Stores at and as of August 28, 2004.
www.anntaylor.com
www.anntaylorLOFT.com
 
