ITEM 1.02 TERMINATION OF A MATERIAL DEFINITIVE AGREEMENT.
 
The employment of Jerome M. Jessup as Senior Executive Vice President for Merchandise and Design at AnnTaylor Stores under his employment agreement with AnnTaylor Stores Corporation (the "Employment Agreement") was terminated on January 10, 2005 in connection with Mr. Jessup's departure from the Company.
 
The terms of Mr. Jessup's severance will be handled under his Employment Agreement, a copy of which was filed as Exhibit 10.2 to the Company's Quarterly Report on Form 10-Q for the quarter ended May 3, 2003, and is incorporated herein by reference.
 
ITEM 8.01 OTHER EVENTS.
 
