Page 2 of 2
 
During the month, the Company opened eight Ann Taylor LOFT stores, and one Ann Taylor Factory store. The total store count at month end was 829, comprised of 364 Ann Taylor stores, 415 Ann Taylor LOFT stores, and 50 Ann Taylor Factory stores. Total square footage at the end of fiscal November 2005 increased 14.3 percent over the same period last year.
 
Ann Taylor is one of the country's leading women's specialty retailers, operating 829 stores in 46 states, the District of Columbia and Puerto Rico, and also Online Stores at and as of November 26, 2005.
