(b) The applicable Borrower shall deliver a notice of continuation/conversion ("") to the Agent not later than 12:00 noon (New York City time) at least three (3) Business Days in advance of the Continuation/Conversion Date, if the Loans are to be converted into or continued as LIBOR Loans and specifying:
