WHEREAS, ATI, ANNCO, ATDS, ATR, the Agent, the lenders referred to therein, the syndication agents named therein, and the issuing banks named therein have entered into that certain $175,000,000 Second Amended and Restated Credit Agreement dated November 14, 2003 (as amended, the "Original Credit Agreement"); and
