(b) In order to comply with Section 304 of the New York Stock Exchange Listed Company Manual requiring that classes of directors be of approximate equal size, James J. Burke, Jr. resigned from the AnnTaylor Stores Corporation (the "Company") Board of Directors as a Class II Director on June 12, 2008 and was simultaneously re-elected as a Class III Director. Mr. Burke was also re-appointed as a member of the Audit Committee and Nominating and Corporate Governance Committee.
